---
title: Carb Smart Fiesta Turkey Salad with Charred Corn Salsa and Chipotle Crema
description: Sweet, spicy and tangy flavors hold court in tihs recipe! Ground turkey is sauteed in a smoky Tex-Mex paste then tossed over fresh spring mix studded with charred corn and tomato salsa. A cooling chipotle crema brings a welcome brightness!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/salade-coloree-de-dinde-e9e71ba1.jpg
